Psalm 122/XX/PR

/SCC/XXOMMENTARY/XX. Psalms 121 and 122 are included from the Sephardic rite.
They are part of a group of pilgrimsò songs, sung by our ancestors as they
went up to the Temple. These two psalms, simple in their language and
strong in their faith, are classics of our ancient religious literature.    /SC/XXA.G./XX/PR

